## ✅ FASE 1 — Fondasi & Auth

### Models yang Difix (13 model)
| Model | Bug Lama | Fix |
|---|---|---|
| [WaliSantri](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/app/Models/WaliSantri.php#16-67) | Missing `use BelongsTo/HasMany` → Fatal Error | Tambah use statements + SoftDeletes + fillable |
| [Student](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/app/Models/Student.php#20-101) | Tidak ada SoftDeletes, relasi kurang | SoftDeletes + relasi histories, attendances, grades |
| [Teacher](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/app/Models/Teacher.php#20-63) | Model kosong total | Fillable + SoftDeletes + is_active + relasi |
| [User](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/app/Models/User.php#24-112) | Fillable kurang `role`, `education_level_id` | Update fillable + helper [isSuperAdmin()](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/app/Models/User.php#69-78), [isGuru()](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/app/Models/User.php#79-87) |
| [AcademicYear](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/app/Models/AcademicYear.php#15-68) | Model kosong | Fillable + casts `is_active` boolean + 3 relasi |
| [GradeLevel](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/app/Models/GradeLevel.php#18-63) | Model kosong | Fillable + relasi classrooms & curriculums |
| [Classroom](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/app/Models/Classroom.php#18-81) | Model kosong | Fillable + relasi waliKelas (FK khusus) |
| [Subject](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/app/Models/Subject.php#18-43) | Model kosong | Fillable + relasi curriculums |
| [Curriculum](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/app/Models/Curriculum.php#23-84) | Model kosong | Fillable + 5 relasi (pivot utama sistem) |
| [StudentHistory](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/app/Models/StudentHistory.php#24-65) | Model kosong | Fillable + 3 relasi BelongsTo |
| [TeacherAssignment](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/app/Models/TeacherAssignment.php#21-79) | Model kosong | Fillable + casts + 4 relasi |
| [Attendance](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/app/Models/Attendance.php#22-63) | Model kosong | Fillable + casts tanggal |
| [Grade](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/app/Models/Grade.php#25-67) | Model kosong | Fillable + casts float nilai |

### Migrations yang Difix (6 file)
| Migration | Perubahan |
|---|---|
| `education_levels` | `kode_tingkat/nama_tingkat` → `kode/nama` |
| `users` | `username` → `name+email`; fix enum role; tambah softDeletes |
| `academic_years` | `kuartal enum(1,2,3)` → `semester enum(Ganjil,Genap)` |
| [classrooms](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/app/Models/GradeLevel.php#43-52) | Nama tabel `'classes'` → `'classrooms'` |
| `student_histories` | FK `classes` → [classrooms](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/app/Models/GradeLevel.php#43-52) |
| `teacher_assignments` | FK `classes` → [classrooms](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/app/Models/GradeLevel.php#43-52) |
| [attendances](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/app/Models/Student.php#83-91) | FK `classes` → [classrooms](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/app/Models/GradeLevel.php#43-52) |

### File Baru Auth System
| File | Fungsi |
|---|---|
| [RoleMiddleware.php](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/app/Http/Middleware/RoleMiddleware.php) | Guard RBAC — validasi role di setiap route |
| [LoginController.php](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/app/Http/Controllers/Auth/LoginController.php) | Login + Logout dengan session security |
| [DashboardController.php](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/app/Http/Controllers/DashboardController.php) | Dashboard adaptif per role |
| [auth/login.blade.php](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/resources/views/auth/login.blade.php) | Halaman login premium |
| [dashboard.blade.php](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/resources/views/dashboard.blade.php) | Dashboard dengan sidebar per role |

### Seeders
- [EducationLevelSeeder](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/database/seeders/EducationLevelSeeder.php#21-45) — 4 unit: TK, MI, MTs, Ulya
- [UserSeeder](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/database/seeders/UserSeeder.php#23-45) — Super Admin: `superadmin@simad.sch.id`
- [AcademicYearSeeder](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/database/seeders/AcademicYearSeeder.php#18-37) — Tahun Ajaran 2025/2026 Ganjil

### Verifikasi Fase 1
```
✅ php artisan migrate:fresh --seed — BERHASIL (16 tabel, 0 error)
✅ Login superadmin berhasil
✅ Redirect ke dashboard berfungsi
```

