## ✅ FASE 2 — Layout Master & Dashboard Data Real

### File Baru
| File | Fungsi |
|---|---|
| [layouts/app.blade.php](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/resources/views/layouts/app.blade.php) | **Layout master reusable** — design system CSS variables, sidebar dinamis per role, topbar dengan info tahun ajaran aktif, flash messages global, semua komponen UI |
| [layouts/auth.blade.php](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/resources/views/layouts/auth.blade.php) | Layout minimalis untuk halaman login/register |
| [errors/403.blade.php](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/resources/views/errors/403.blade.php) | Halaman error Forbidden (RBAC) |
| [errors/404.blade.php](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/resources/views/errors/404.blade.php) | Halaman error Not Found |

### Perubahan File
| File | Perubahan |
|---|---|
| [dashboard.blade.php](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/resources/views/dashboard.blade.php) | Refactor → `@extends('layouts.app')`, data real dari DB, tabel ringkasan per unit, hero card |
| [auth/login.blade.php](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/resources/views/auth/login.blade.php) | Refactor → `@extends('layouts.auth')`, DRY & clean |
| [DashboardController.php](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/app/Http/Controllers/DashboardController.php) | Query data real: [getGlobalStats()](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/app/Http/Controllers/DashboardController.php#63-85) + [getUnitStats()](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/app/Http/Controllers/DashboardController.php#86-118) per role |
| [routes/web.php](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/routes/web.php) | Tambah route placeholder Fase 3 agar sidebar tidak error |

### Verifikasi Fase 2
```
✅ Dashboard tampil dengan layout baru (sidebar, topbar)
✅ Topbar menampilkan "2025/2026 — Ganjil" dari database
✅ Tabel "Ringkasan per Unit": TK, MI, MTs, Ulya tampil (data real)
✅ Klik "Data Guru" di sidebar → pesan "Fase 3 segera hadir" muncul
✅ Error pages 403 & 404 siap
```

